title: Desktop vacuum packaging machine US-DZ-320
short_description: Bulky vacuum packaging equipment may be inconvenient for some, or less expensive vacuum packaging equipment that is smaller in size and less expensive than its larger counterparts. This US-DZ-320 model packing machine is compact and convenient. Voltage 220-110V, power 0.32 kW, camera size 355*340*70 mm, weight 28 kg; dimensions: length 460 mm, width 390 mm and height 390 mm.
short_description_uz: Katta hajmli vakumli qadoqlash uskunalari ba'zilar uchun noqulaylik tug'diradi yoki kichikroq hajmli va kattalariga nisbatan narxi ham pastroq bo'lgan vakumli qadoqlash uskunasi asqotadi. Ushbu US-DZ-320 modeldagi qadoqlash uskunasi ixcham va qulaydir. Kuchlanishi 220-110V, quvvati 0.32 kW, kamera o'lchami 355*340*70 mm, vazni 28 kg; o'lchamlari: uzunligi 460 mm, kengligi 390 mm va balandligi ham 390 mm ni tashkil etadi.
